metadata.name: Bored.Ai Collective MemberChip #1
metadata.description: The Bored.Ai Collective is dedicated to giving its members creative superpowers, beginning with a collection of 10,000 MemberChips - NFTs which grant access to cutting-edge artificial intelligence (Ai). Your MemberChip NFT doubles as your ticket to the Bored.Ai Collective, and gets you exclusive access to members-only spaces and perks, and NFT drops - the first of which is the debut Text2Art collection. Visit https://bored.ai for more information.
